item_category: Three years of software and security updates are supported by a threeyear warranty, so you can keep your phone out of landfill and in your hands for longer. The 100% compostable case, designed to be hard on the ground and soft on the Earth, is included for additional protection. Our 64MP quad camera with ZEISS Optics and AI assist lets you shoot cinematic quality footage of grand landscapes, phenomenal close-ups, and vibrant portraits. There are also tools for colour-grading and mode settings to help enhance your story.
